{"tid":1583782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慶祝曾獻屎傳火十周年暨被毛魔召見 (請勿用曾記吊頸帶)","createTime":"2019-09-20T19:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T12:10:45.000Z","uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a35bc15bb728eee7adb4d366159b1f3950ea7f7c","tid":1583782,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Yk_lTqKMqlY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYk_lTqKMqlY&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1w9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=5f786b03\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Yk_lTqKMqlY</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係阿傻 跛腳學舉火<br />\n真正爛鬼傻的狂的就即係阿傻<br />\n佢年前晌內地割腎移植<br />\n識得日日淫笑呵呵<br />\n失禁係咁屙屙屙<br />\n生意係織紅的藍的吊頸帶何其多<br />\n行埋就嗌晒「中国万岁」博鬧民主各派<br />\n面色紅色掙爆血管就死賴個籮<br />\n<br />\n陷身失禁亂屙<br />\n鴨罐都裝足屎了又再屙篤囉<br />\n舉火都用錢買得無錢無得有錢無不<br />\n用晒巨富買位上黎同慶賀<br />\n祝你冚家寶福山上木棺同運夠晒妥<br />\n嘿 四口合棺亦可銅棺跳樓跳樓長開長哀<br />\n又怕黑呢你做阿傻"},{"pid":"259b3c1580733e29f99d43842387c94c8567d253","tid":1583782,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T19:28:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"b47d5b2ae60bb9aad04cdc138ebd124985b9aca1","tid":1583782,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5dfd7e16610aa77b470b0e1e4da05348da2ba18","tid":1583782,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T12:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}